sentences: In 2003, Draw released his first album, The City.
A second album, Train 64, was released in 2006; it was named after the Via Rail train route between Montreal and Toronto.
He then recorded a third album, Adagio, which was released in 2007, and toured in Canada to support it.
Draw represented Canada at the World Expo in Shanghai, China in the summer of 2010.
